# S01-T04: Setup Core Zustand Stores

## Objective
Create the foundational Zustand stores for telemetry, UI state, and configuration.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/features/telemetry/stores/useTelemetryStore.ts` — TelemetryData state, connected flag
- `src/features/hud/stores/useHudStore.ts` — Slot visibility (7 slots), debug mode toggle
- `src/features/debug/stores/useDebugStore.ts` — FPS, video config, ffplay command preview
- All stores use Zustand slices pattern (no monolithic store)
- TypeScript interfaces for all store shapes
- Stores match the data contracts from drone-interface/6 telemetry_simulator.rs

## Reference
- Telemetry shape: `drone-interface/6/src/types/index.ts` (TelemetryData interface)
- Store patterns: `drone-interface/6/src/stores/telemetry.ts`, `debugPanel.ts`, `theme.ts`

## Steps
1. Define TelemetryData, HudState, DebugState, ConfigState interfaces
2. Create each store with Zustand `create()`
3. Add devtools middleware for debugging
4. Export typed selector hooks
